{"tid":1047720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"先免費入住 再𠱁轉名「防爭產」 牧師涉騙女教友1,900萬樓","createTime":"2019-03-05T06:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T09:11:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0a104df861ad38f137ca8b2e2b092d49b097fa74","tid":1047720,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:57:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190305/20626305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F20626305&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=97026344\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F20626305&h=3a493500\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190305/20626305</a><br />\n<br />\n先免費入住 再𠱁轉名「防爭產」<br />\n牧師涉騙女教友1,900萬樓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190305/large/05la7p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190305%2Flarge%2F05la7p01.jpg&h=97cbd9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告曾繼才稱當年原告懇求他入住涉案單位。夏家朗攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】聖公會諸聖座堂退休牧師曾繼才被指以退休後「得嗰400萬，夠食唔夠住」等各種藉口，於十年間先後騙得年老女教友提供跑馬地物業供他居住，又照顧兩人醫療和生活使費，甚至借錢予其小姨解決財困，涉款共多達460萬元。女教友更聽信牧師之言，為免日後被繼子女爭樓而將物業暫時轉名給牧師一家，但對方不肯歸還，物業現市值1,900萬元。牧師反駁指兩夫婦「懇求他入住」，又自言是知足常樂的人，不會貪心。案件昨在高院聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n記者：蔡少玲<br />\n<br />\n原告黎驍敏現年72歲，被告分別為退休牧師曾繼才、其妻劉俠英和小姨劉俠賢，三人年齡約由78至80歲。原告現向被告追討涉案跑馬地樂苑大廈單位，至於多年來給被告的460多萬元，則只追討其中62萬元。<br />\n<br />\n根據原告案情，她於1990年婚後隨丈夫到旺角諸聖座堂崇拜，曾為該教會牧師。2004年時即將退休的曾常埋怨獲教會400萬元退休金，「夠食唔夠住，夠住唔夠食」，原告稱有物業可免租供他住。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：稱小姨財困 借百萬落格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190305/large/a0701a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190305%2Flarge%2Fa0701a.gif&h=79182ac1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾承諾隨時歸還物業<br />\n<br />\n曾與妻及小姨三人於翌年入住該800呎物業，原告更騙丈夫以1.3萬元租予曾。曾繼才昨在庭上供稱，當年教會有提供物業讓他退休後以3,000元租住，故他曾拒絕原告好意，惟原告夫婦「好熱誠咁叫我入去住」，他才接受。原告方指2008年原告丈夫去世後，曾繼才游說她立遺囑，以免丈夫跟他亡妻所生的子女跟她爭樓，原告遂請三被告作為遺產承辦人，翌年更將樂苑單位轉給三被告。原告指曾承諾日後若有需要可隨時歸還物業。曾昨斬釘截鐵稱絕無說過，但承認從沒交租。對於曾否向原告提過「夠食唔夠住」的一番說話，曾表示「應該冇，唔記得」，他只承認2009年與妻、小姨和兩名子女及兩名孫兒共收過原告290萬元，「嗰啲係gift嚟」。他多次強調自己是牧師，「冇諗住住大屋」，崇尚簡樸生活，不會貪心，「上帝會眷顧我」，又謂原告視他如「大佬」。法官追問曾為何原告突將物業轉名給他們，曾答估計是「對我特別好，所以分身家畀我」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方問他，若原告因為投資失利要求他歸還物業，他可會照辦時，曾支吾以對，後稱「冇諗過呢個問題」。聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA142/17  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n違感化令青年逃出法庭<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n稱小姨財困 借百萬落格<br />\n<br />\n稱小姨財困 借百萬落格"},{"pid":"f32b104f541cdb52c6112c7451e438a9d00a128c","tid":1047720,"uid":87741,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"信耶穌嘅人咁蠢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話有主保佑㗎咩？<br />\n主去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ea802b570745610d0dccc0ef2160fdff16931f","tid":1047720,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"30萬睇牙....<br />\nbtw 點可以咁有錢"},{"pid":"1ede289ee4b2487db09a462742b87e14b79e91cb","tid":1047720,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"最慘係D子女"},{"pid":"bd83af37721efc8cd9c02757f4a9ba169c55c2c5","tid":1047720,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:07:17.000Z","msg":"一定又係耶穌既恩賜啦"},{"pid":"83bd16f69984031de9a8982531e398081f95722b","tid":1047720,"uid":73310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:08:37.000Z","msg":"神嘅考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8cd5dc467998fe3e098a03f3e84a29a85c185d","tid":1047720,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:10:02.000Z","msg":"果然人如其名，曾繼財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04b5dd8be7a18c87b9996c3ffe3ecd586019414","tid":1047720,"uid":237425,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:20:49.000Z","msg":"他多次強調自己是牧師，「冇諗住住大屋」，崇尚簡樸生活，不會貪心，<br />\n<br />\n法官追問曾為何原告突將物業轉名給他們，曾答估計是「對我特別好，所以分身家畀我」。<br />\n<br />\n話自己唔貪心，但拎左人1900萬跑馬地800呎樓<br />\n仲有錢400萬<br />\n真係幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b7a749ab0020101095628e8e61ca03f73305a4","tid":1047720,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:24:05.000Z","msg":"佢已經達到左&ldquo;唔洗爭產&rdquo;呢個要求"},{"pid":"e12344e4616de268165db76983afcf964a279913","tid":1047720,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f284992382eb037105bef0d37510a33cc2f8f4e4","tid":1047720,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:45:43.000Z","msg":"比層樓我係主既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927ff033569741440c1c16f82d0301614611e1d7","tid":1047720,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f04b5dd8be7a18c87b9996c3ffe3ecd586019414","tid":1047720,"uid":237425,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:20:49.000Z","msg":"他多次強調自己是牧師，「冇諗住住大屋」，崇尚簡樸生活，不會貪心，<br />\n<br />\n法官追問曾為何原告突將物業轉名給他們，曾答估計是「對我特別好，所以分身家畀我」。<br />\n<br />\n話自己唔貪心，但拎左人1900萬跑馬地800呎樓<br />\n仲有錢400萬<br />\n真係幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"我唔貪心架，1900萬既樓加埋400萬就夠架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38259b1aa6b28175f6d15fde19d6916cf3fbe2a4","tid":1047720,"uid":139215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"神指使猶大陰呀耶穌一獲呀嘛<br />\n我記得個劇情"},{"pid":"e596a0ec3c898a17facf5c3a036e2c475d378dcd","tid":1047720,"uid":123591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f32b104f541cdb52c6112c7451e438a9d00a128c","tid":1047720,"uid":87741,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"信耶穌嘅人咁蠢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話有主保佑㗎咩？<br />\n主去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T07:49:55.000Z","msg":"聰明就唔信耶蘇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e478431b3da96b30a3acd337a276ff90f20a40d8","tid":1047720,"uid":190129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:01:14.000Z","msg":"蠢人都咁有錢，不過都算有運 72歲先比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ba0a3ca93f38865f7ef02902917da81177dd3e","tid":1047720,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"上帝只會幫助罪人"},{"pid":"8ab7165cd9b3457b4b91db6c510803f8be322a71","tid":1047720,"uid":171611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"真。繼財"},{"pid":"7cf1541ad31902998abdc96097c8b230264b567f","tid":1047720,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f32b104f541cdb52c6112c7451e438a9d00a128c","tid":1047720,"uid":87741,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"信耶穌嘅人咁蠢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話有主保佑㗎咩？<br />\n主去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:13:35.000Z","msg":"主能夠主能夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877ad3f3fab5a9c88029afad4a3f11cd646c2912","tid":1047720,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"女大律師都可以咁on9，被牧師迷惑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>退休牧師涉騙女教友案女大狀突私訊抱不平 控辯爭議應否擱置審訊</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%B6%89%E9%A8%99%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%8F%8B%E6%A1%88%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E7%AA%81%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E6%8A%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B3-%E6%8E%A7%E8%BE%AF%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%87%89%E5%90%A6%E6%93%B1%E7%BD%AE%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A-055400941.html?fbclid=IwAR0DP3xlmrKOxy0DtkrzK4iT85xaSdRcUULCnxKpkXNIJoofTz0yceLGHuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258B%2580%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A7%2581%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%258A%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%2593%25B1%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25A8%258A-055400941.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0DP3xlmrKOxy0DtkrzK4iT85xaSdRcUULCnxKpkXNIJoofTz0yceLGHuY&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=ce882d77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%B6%89%E9%A8%99%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%8F%8B%E6%A1%88%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E7%AA%81%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E6%8A%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B3-%E6%8E%A7%E8%BE%AF%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%87%89%E5%90%A6%E6%93%B1%E7%BD%AE%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A-055400941.html?fbclid=IwAR0DP3xlmrKOxy0DtkrzK4iT85xaSdRcUULCnxKpkXNIJoofTz0yceLGHuY</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】高等法院今早審理一宗物業糾紛案期間，爆出有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>與案無關的女大狀「私訊」法官影響審訊的事件</strong></span></span>。案件原涉聖公會諸聖座堂一名退休牧師，他被指多年前向女教友「呃食呃住」，騙得對方提供跑馬地物業予其夫婦自住，並借錢予小姨解財困。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有傳媒昨報道審訊後，女大狀今晨1時突然向主審法官發電郵為被告牧師抱不平。</span></span></strong>控辯雙方今早在庭上爭議應否擱置審訊，法官坦言此決定將比判案更難，暫將案押後至今午，再決定是否安排重審。<br />\n<br />\n案件3名被告依次為聖公會諸聖座堂退休牧師曾繼才、曾的妻子劉俠英和小姨劉俠賢。曾繼才被指在退休後以不同藉口，誘使原告人黎驍敏為他兩夫婦供住供食，並將一個跑馬地物業轉至牧師名下。曾繼才辯稱，涉事物業是原告人給他的贈禮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">曾繼才原定今早繼續接受盤問，但主審本案的暫委法官林定國於今晨1時收到一名女大狀的電郵，解釋原告人借貸予牧師全是出於好意，又指<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">案件在傳媒報道後或影響教會聲譽</span>，期盼林官英明判斷。</span><br />\n<br />\n原告方透露，<span style=\"color: red;\">該名女大狀是涉事教會高層，亦是富有經驗的大律師</span>，與林官在同一辦事處（chamber）工作。原告方指該名女大狀並非獨立的第三者，涉嫌妨礙司法公正，林官若繼續審理本案，或會造成明顯偏見（apparent bias），故要求案件交另一法官重審。辯方則反對申請，又指排期重審對被告不公。<br />\n<br />\n林官坦言他私下認識該名女大狀，是他在辦事處的朋友，但已有一段相當長時間無見面。他表明會忽略電郵內容，但承認現階段中止審訊或影響司法公義，而他繼續審理本案或予偏袒觀感。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：黃梓生"},{"pid":"e47aa8305e7710de369470e345aa19ac71eb9ef1","tid":1047720,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"877ad3f3fab5a9c88029afad4a3f11cd646c2912","tid":1047720,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"女大律師都可以咁on9，被牧師迷惑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>退休牧師涉騙女教友案女大狀突私訊抱不平 控辯爭議應否擱置審訊</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%B6%89%E9%A8%99%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%8F%8B%E6%A1%88%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E7%AA%81%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E6%8A%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B3-%E6%8E%A7%E8%BE%AF%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%87%89%E5%90%A6%E6%93%B1%E7%BD%AE%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A-055400941.html?fbclid=IwAR0DP3xlmrKOxy0DtkrzK4iT85xaSdRcUULCnxKpkXNIJoofTz0yceLGHuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258B%2580%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A7%2581%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%258A%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%2593%25B1%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25A8%258A-055400941.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0DP3xlmrKOxy0DtkrzK4iT85xaSdRcUULCnxKpkXNIJoofTz0yceLGHuY&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak46aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=ce882d77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%B6%89%E9%A8%99%E5%A5%B3%E6%95%99%E5%8F%8B%E6%A1%88%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E7%AA%81%E7%A7%81%E8%A8%8A%E6%8A%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%B9%B3-%E6%8E%A7%E8%BE%AF%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%87%89%E5%90%A6%E6%93%B1%E7%BD%AE%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A-055400941.html?fbclid=IwAR0DP3xlmrKOxy0DtkrzK4iT85xaSdRcUULCnxKpkXNIJoofTz0yceLGHuY</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】高等法院今早審理一宗物業糾紛案期間，爆